In this bizarre, post-modern version of L. Brank Baum&#039;s novel &#039;The Wonderful Wizard of Oz&#039; and the classic movie based on the book, &#039;The Wizard of Oz&#039;, Zooey Deschanel stars as DG, the main character who finds herself trapped in a place called the O.Z. or the Outer Zone. There she searches for her parents and is joined in her travels by Glitch, a man who has had half of his brain taken away because of something he knew, Raw, a member of a species called the "viewers" who read emotions and heal, and Cain - a "Tin Man" (which was the name of the police force in the O.Z. before the witch, Azkadellia took over, taken from their sheriff&#039;s tin badges) who seeks revenge for the damage done to his heart.
